---

<Layout
  title="Portfolio | Camille's Digital Marketing"
  description="Explore my portfolio of successful digital marketing projects and case studies."
>
  <div class="space-y-16">
    <PageHero
      title="Portfolio"
      subtitle="Explore my work and successful client projects"
    />

    <!-- Introduction Section -->
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold">My Work</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Browse through a selection of my most successful projects. Each
        represents a unique challenge and demonstrates my approach to creating
        effective digital marketing solutions that deliver real results.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Metrics Section -->
    <section class="bg-base-200 py-12">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          {
            metrics.map((metric) => (
              <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-md">
                <div class="card-body items-center text-center">
                  <div class="text-primary mb-2">
                    <Icon name={metric.icon} class="h-12 w-12" />
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-4xl font-bold">{metric.value}</p>
                  <p class="text-base-content/70">{metric.label}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Portfolio Grid -->
    <section class="py-12">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4">
        <h2 class="mb-10 text-center text-2xl font-bold">Featured Projects</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          {
            portfolioItems.map((item) => (
              <PortfolioItem
                title={item.title}
                client={item.client}
                category={item.category}
                imagePlaceholder={item.imagePlaceholder}
                tags={item.tags}
              >
                {item.description}
              </PortfolioItem>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials Section with Carousel -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-center text-3xl font-bold">Client Testimonials</h2>
        <p class="text-base-content/80 mx-auto mb-12 max-w-2xl text-center">
          See what our clients have to say about their experience working with
          us
        </p>

        <TestimonialCarousel testimonials={testimonials} />
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Process Section -->
    <section class="px-4 py-12">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-bold">My Approach to Projects</h2>
        <p class="mb-10">
          Every project follows a structured process to ensure we achieve the
          best possible results.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-md">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="mb-4 flex items-center">
                <div
                  class="bg-primary text-primary-content mr-4 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full"
                >
                  <span class="font-bold">1</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Discovery & Research</h3>
              </div>
              <p>
                I begin by understanding your business, goals, target audience,
                and competitors to establish a solid foundation for the project.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-md">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="mb-4 flex items-center">
                <div
                  class="bg-primary text-primary-content mr-4 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full"
                >
                  <span class="font-bold">2</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Strategy Development</h3>
              </div>
              <p>
                Based on research insights, I create a customized strategy
                tailored to your specific needs and objectives.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-md">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="mb-4 flex items-center">
                <div
                  class="bg-primary text-primary-content mr-4 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full"
                >
                  <span class="font-bold">3</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Implementation</h3>
              </div>
              <p>
                Once the strategy is approved, I execute the plan with attention
                to detail and regular communication throughout.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card bg-base-100 shadow-md">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="mb-4 flex items-center">
                <div
                  class="bg-primary text-primary-content mr-4 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-full"
                >
                  <span class="font-bold">4</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="card-title">Analysis & Optimization</h3>
              </div>
              <p>
                I continuously monitor performance, provide regular reports, and
                optimize the strategy based on data and results.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action -->
    <CallToAction
      title="Ready to Create Your Success Story?"
      buttonText="Let's Work Together"
      buttonLink="/contact"
    >
      I'd love to help you achieve your digital marketing goals. Contact me
      today to discuss how we can work together on your next project.
    </CallToAction>
  </div>
</Layout>
